{"tid":148410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[咪FF啦］回應Roadshow停播傳聞　九巴：車廂電視代理權年中約滿　現正招標","createTime":"2017-03-08T14:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T07:07:46.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04d9a03d34cb7a38d9e1a54428d066a4d9978392","tid":148410,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"昨日有傳九巴車廂電視 RoadShow（路訊通）將會停播，九巴今日回覆查詢時證實，流動多媒體廣告服務的代理權將於今年年中屆滿，目前正在招標。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 巴士專頁 「Buscess」日前引述「內部員工」消息稱，路訊通營業部員工的僱傭合約，由長工轉為合約制，短期合約則會於今年六月底完結，稱有指 RoadShow 將會於今年六月停播。<br />\n<br />\n九巴今日向本網證實正在招標的消息，但稱對其他網傳消息，不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n去年上半年，路訊通虧損近 1200萬元。同年十二月中，路訊通公佈委任資深傳媒人、前 DBC 行政總裁羅燦，出任路訊通董事總經理兼執行董事，今年二月一日生效。羅燦加盟的消息，一度令不獲投資者<br />\n關注的路訊通股價上升逾四成。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4-%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E6%AC%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%B4%84%E6%BB%BF-%E7%8F%BE%E6%AD%A3%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%25BB%25BF-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%25A8%2599%2F&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=46e6cafa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%2582%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%25BB%25BF-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%25A8%2599%2F&h=eda80f98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4-%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%82%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E6%AC%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E7%B4%84%E6%BB%BF-%E7%8F%BE%E6%AD%A3%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99/</a>"},{"pid":"f5f97dff9b1a0384687e41eb1d0c